Why AGPL-3.0
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
This project bundles and modifies the Odysseus self-hosted AI workspace by
PewDiePie (Felix Kjellberg), which is licensed AGPL-3.0-or-later:

    https://github.com/pewdiepie-archdaemon/odysseus

Because the combined work includes AGPL-3.0 source and is served to users over
a network, OpenClaw Workspace as a whole is distributed under AGPL-3.0. Under
AGPL-3.0 section 13, an operator who runs a modified version and lets users
interact with it remotely over a network must offer those users the
Corresponding Source of the running version.

